relation: Publication containing journal articles written by St. Cloud State faculty and students, covering a wide variety of topics mostly related to public education, as well as containing about alumni, students, faculty, and campus events related to St. Cloud State. Articles include "Thought Analysis of 'The Vision of Sir Launfal,'" continuation of "Questions on the Philosophy of Education" and "Influence of Forest Trees on Living Water."
